condition.narrative: Submission of report by MOF internal auditors on post payment audits and review of Project's financial management system no laterthan 45 days after each quarter reviewed
The Borrower shall appoint a Supervisory Board, satisfactory to IDA, for the newly corporate DABM
The Borrower shall ensure that relevant documentation such as bank statements, AFMIS reports & any other information required byPMF to prepare financial reports are made available to PMF upon request
The Borrower shall ensure that the Project will be implemented in accordance with the streamlined procedures established under theMOU.
The Borrower shall hire and, throughout the period of implementation of the Project, maintain PMF.
